These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, july, february, august
4 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, snooker, poker
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, aconite, begonia
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, horse, rat
 1. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in november is in an even position##4
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 5. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the person playing poker##2
10. the person who's birthday is in november is the owner of the rat##1
11. the person playing snooker is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | february  | november    | august    | july   |
| Game   | mah-jongg     | billiard   | snooker       | poker    |
| Flower   | sunflower | dahlia | begonia    | aconite |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | chinchilla | horse     |

