.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, animation, horror, family
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, march, july, february
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, old-henry, pall-mall, cain
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the old-henry-smoker##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
 7. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the dannemann-smoker##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's birthday is in july is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre          | scientific  | animation    | horror     | family       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| Birthday   | july | december   | march   | february    |
| Cigar         | pall-mall | cain  | dannemann | old-henry   |

