.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
City: miami, berlin, hamburg, paris
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, paramedic, social-worker, writer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, zinnia, amaryllis, rose
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, camping, photography, card-games
 1. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 2. the person who growszinnia is the social-worker##1
 3. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
 4. the librarian is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is the writer##1
 6. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person who growsrose##1
 8. the writer is in an even position##4
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person traveling to hamburg##1
11. the person traveling to miami is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| City      | miami | hamburg   | paris    | berlin      |
| Job           | social-worker | librarian | paramedic | writer     |
| Flower   | zinnia      | rose   | bellflower   | amaryllis |
| Hobby           | card-games         | cooking       | photography  | camping       |

