.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, pony, frog
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, plum, zucchini
House: palace, ranch-style, wooden, cape-cod
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, june, march
 1. the owner of the bird is the person eating corn##1
 2. the wooden house is on the left of the palace house##1
 3. the person eating corn is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 4. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
 5. the owner of the fish is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 8. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is the ranch-style house##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the palace house##1
11. the owner of the pony is the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Pet   | frog       | pony   | bird   | fish   |
| Food       | lime        | zucchini | corn    | plum       |
| House      | cape-cod | ranch-style    | wooden  | palace |
| Birthday      | november  | june  | december | march    |

