.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, orange, pineapple, spinach
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, snowmobile, trike, taxi
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, soul, folk
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, juice, hot-chocolate, coffee
 1. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person driving the trike is between the person drinking milk and the person eating spinach##2
 3. the fan of soul is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 4. the fan of r&b is the person eating kiwi##1
 5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 6. the person driving the van is in an even position##4
 7. the person eating orange is the fan of ambient##1
 8. the person driving the trike is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
10. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
11. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
12. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Food    | pineapple    | spinach      | kiwi          | orange    |
| Transport   | snowmobile | taxi       | trike | van |
| Music-Genre     | folk     | soul      | r&b     | ambient |
| Beverage   | juice   | coffee | hot-chocolate        | milk   |

