.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, grey, emerald, light-blue
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, accountant, architect, photographer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, folk, gospel
City: london, nizza, new-york, paris
 1. the architect is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
 2. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
 3. the designer is on the right of the accountant##1
 4. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
 5. the person who likes coral is in an odd position##4
 6. the fan of gospel is between the person traveling to new-york and the fan of dubstep##2
 7. the fan of folk is the architect##1
 8. the person who likes grey is the architect##1
 9. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Color      | emerald  | grey    | coral       | light-blue       |
| Job          | photographer    | architect | accountant | designer     |
| Music-Genre   | classical | folk        | gospel    | dubstep   |
| City   | london  | new-york      | paris    | nizza |

