The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, marigold, sunflower, daffodil
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, subway, trike
 1. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in january##3
 5. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
11. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
12. the person who growsiris is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | snooker | billiard    | canasta  | bridge      |
| Birthday   | january      | june | december | july   |
