.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, golf, badminton, soccer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy, sports, zombie
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, eggplant, grapefruit, garlic
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, dunhill, vegafina, bluemaster
 1. the bluemaster-smoker is in an odd position##4
 2. the cain-smoker is between the bluemaster-smoker and the vegafina-smoker##2
 3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 4. the person watching sports movies is in an odd position##4
 5. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
 7. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
 8. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 9. the cain-smoker is between the person eating pineapple and the person watching fantasy movies##2
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
11. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
12. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Sport         | golf  | badminton    | surfing    | soccer |
| Movie-Genre   | sports   | epic       | fantasy  | zombie    |
| Food   | pineapple | eggplant | grapefruit | garlic   |
| Cigar           | vegafina    | cain        | bluemaster   | dunhill    |

