City: paris, nizza, liverpool, edinburgh
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of folk is between the craftsman house and the person traveling to nizza##2
 4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 5. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 6. the craftsman house is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 7. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is the craftsman house##1
 9. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
10. the futuristic house is on the right of the cottage house##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of house is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the fan of indie is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage          | tea     | milk      | hot-chocolate  | mirinda        |
| House   | craftsman     | cottage | futuristic | modern      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | folk        | jazz        | indie        |
| City         | edinburgh | paris    | nizza      | liverpool |

