 3. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is in an odd position##4
 6. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 9. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
12. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

