The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, electrician, journalist, videographer
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, canasta, go
 1. the videographer is in an odd position##4
 2. the videographer is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
 3. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the dancer##3
 4. the person playing go is between the person drinking almond-milk and the journalist##2
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is the person drinking mirinda##1
