 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the electrician is on the left or right of the person playing go##3
 9. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
10. the person playing mah-jongg is the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
12. the dancer is on the left or right of the electrician##3
13. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |   3    |     4      |
