.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, metal, techno, electronic
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, video-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, jet-ski, skateboard, tram
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, argentine, brazilian, colombian
 1. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the colombian is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
 3. the person driving the subway is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
 5. the pakistani is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the far right##1
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
10. the brazilian is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
11. the person driving the tram is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Music-Genre      | techno       | metal | ambient        | electronic        |
| Hobby         | video-games | singing       | card-games | photography |
| Transport   | tram     | jet-ski        | subway    | skateboard      |
| Nationality         | argentine     | brazilian    | colombian | pakistani   |

