.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, birdd-games, traveling, filmmaking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, water, juice
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, parkour, rugby, water-polo
4 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, dog, goldfish
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking juice##2
 3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
 4. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the person who's hobby is birdd-games is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
 8. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
10. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
12. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby   | birdd-games      | dancing | filmmaking     | traveling        |
| Beverage   | water | juice  | soy-milk     | tea |
| Sport         | parkour    | cycling | rugby      | water-polo |
| Pet     | goldfish | bird     | dog | hamster       |

 